UPDATE
  Show when the next game update runs.

SYNTAX
  update
  upda

DESCRIPTION
  Displays the current server time, the scheduled time for the next
  update, and a countdown.

  The update is the heartbeat of the game.  Each update cycle:
    - Sectors produce goods (food, iron, LCM, gold, etc.)
    - Population grows or shrinks
    - Efficiency builds toward 100% in designated sectors
    - Distribution and delivery move commodities automatically
    - Ships, planes, and land units regain mobility
    - Tech, research, education, and happiness levels change
    - Military reserve ages slightly (1% per 24 ETU)
    - Enlistment centers auto-recruit civilians to military

  Updates run on a fixed interval (shown by the 'update' command).
  In a standard game this is 60 minutes / 60 ETU.

EXAMPLE
  update                    see next update time and countdown

